It is up to us to offer praises to the
Source of all, to declare the great-
ness of the author of Creation, who
has made us different from the
other nations of the earth, and situ-
ated us in quite a different spot, and
made our daily lot another kind
from theirs, and given us a destiny
uncommon in this world./PR
